{
  "stem": "9702.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, anyhow, for me, it was easier, in a way, because I had somebody to look, look out after me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father used to go and find another place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't stay in the houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We stayed in the, in the barns and the-- what do you call the place-- the barn where they keep food for the, for the, for the horses and for the--",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we used to make a hole-- my father used to make a hole in the, in the, in the hay or in the straw.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to hid there and lay there all day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at night, whatever we had to do, we had to wait until at night .",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father used to go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was in hiding 19 months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- the first winter in '42, it was a terrible, hard winter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was in November.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first snow fell out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were by somebody in the barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And somebody told the German, the Ukrainian, that there were Jews in that villages.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one morning, they surrounded the whole village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were looking for Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So naturally, we had-- where we were, we had to go away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we went away to somebody else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, at night, and we hid again in the straw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they didn't know that we are there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We laid there for about three, four-- I think it's for about four days and three nights.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's-- we didn't have no-- I mean, we had a little food, so it was finished.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the worst thing was the water, terrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The tap water was off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Finally, my father said it's going to go out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And while-- and they did surrounded that, that Czech village.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
